  <brief_title>An Investigational Drug, Crizotinib (PF-02341066), Is Being Studied In Tumors, Except Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer, That Are Positive For Anaplastic Lymphoma Kinase (ALK)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 1b Open-label Study Of The Safety And Clinical Activity Of Crizotinib (Pf-02341066) In Tumors With Genetic Events Involving The Anaplastic Lymphoma Kinase (Alk ) Gene Locus</official_title>
